            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThe%20prayer%20of%20Jabez%20is%20a%20cry%20for%20deliverance%20from%20a%20life%20of%20pain.%20The%20name%20Jabez%20means%20%22distress%2C%22%20or%20%22pain%2C%22%20and%20accordingly%2C%20from%20the%20day%20of%20his%20birth%2C%20Jabez%20endured%20much%20pain.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESatan%20seeks%20to%20afflict%20those%20who%20are%20honorable%20with%20pain%20and%20sorrow%20in%20order%20to%20destroy%20their%20effectiveness.%20Jabez%20prayed%20for%20God%20to%20turn%20the%20devil's%20curse%20into%20blessing%20and%20his%20own%20limitations%20into%20enlargement.%20Our%20prayers%2C%20too%2C%20should%20be%20for%20God%20to%20enlarge%20our%20territory%20just%20as%20He%20did%20for%20Jabez%2C%20who%20had%20been%20through%20such%20pain%20and%20sorrow.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20enlarged%2C%20not%20for%20personal%20pride%20and%20pleasure%2C%20but%20to%20reach%20into%20the%20regions%20beyond%20with%20the%20Gospel.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJabez%20also%20prayed%20that%20God%20would%20keep%20him%20from%20harm%20so%20he%20could%20be%20delivered%20from%20a%20life%20of%20pain%2C%20sorrow%2C%20and%20distraction.%20And%20God%20granted%20his%20request!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhy%20not%20pray%20today%20for%20God%20to%20reverse%20the%20curse%20and%20break%20the%20limitations%20you%20have%20faced%2C%20perhaps%20even%20from%20birth%3F%20He%20will%20spread%20His%20protection%20over%20you%20(Psalm%205%3A11)%20and%20surround%20you%20with%20favor%20as%20with%20a%20shield%20(v.%2012)!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
